import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import '../static/seatmap.css'; export default function SeatMap () { const [count, setCount] = useState(0); const click = () => { const seats = document.querySelectorAll('.row .seat:not(.occupied)'); seats.forEach(seat => { seat.addEventListener('click', (e) => { if (seat.classList.contains('selected')) { seat.classList.remove('selected'); setCount(prev => prev - 1); } else { seat.classList.add('selected'); setCount(prev => prev + 1); } }); }); }; useEffect(() => { click() }, [count]) return (
  • N/A
  • Selected
  • Occupied

Selected {count} for a price of Ksh: 0

); }
